data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. In the beautiful community of Poinciana Villages, you'll find this appealing single family residence ready for someone new to call it home. A path of gorgeous pavers makes up the driveway and front walkway, welcoming you to the property in style. Once inside, you're greeted by a spacious open floor plan, with grand ceilings and an abundance of natural light. The kitchen is a cook's dream, with stone countertops, a bar top, stone facade on the island and backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. The primary suite includes a large sleeping area, ensuite bathroom, and walk in closet. A large sliding glass door provides access to the covered patio as well as the lush backyard ready for some Florida fun. This property has been maintained beautifully and is ready for a new owner to make this their home. Contact the listing agent to schedule a viewing.
